					"type": 23,
					"value": "The Visage of Guilt standing in front of several skeletons (dead adventurers that found their end by the hands of the Tollhouse Collector).\r\n\r\nSpeaks with the same voice as the shadow-cursed tollmaster, but with a distinct emotional inflection. Guilt, in this case."
